name: TUA-173
description: TUA-173 Verify that the ‘Опис’ text field is filled in with valid data
descriptionHtml: TUA-173 Verify that the ‘Опис’ text field is filled in with valid data

testStage.description: TUA-173 Verify that the ‘Опис’ text field is filled in with valid data

steps.name: Authorize user with valid email admin@gmail.com and password admin
Click on dropdown for authorized user in top right corner of header
Click on 'Мій профіль' button in dropdown for authorized users
Click 6 times on upper arrow in 'Від' field
Click 7 times on upper arrow in 'до' field
Enter 9632548777 data into Phone number field of 'Контакти' area
Fill 'Опис' field with Education, students, Школа балетуee and so

parameters.name: text
parameters.value: Education, students, Школа балетуee and so
